Cleveland Bitcoin
description: The Cleveland Bitcoin Club has public, free meetups twice a month. One is typically a bar/social meetup and another is an education/demonstration/planning type meetup at a Public Library. Cleveland Bitcoin hosted the 2024 Halving Party at Town Hall in Ohio City in April 2024 with 60+ attendees and several vendors who accept Bitcoin attended. All are welcome - Bitcoin only.
